stories.text:
StoneDB is an open-source hybrid transaction&#x2F;analytical processing (HTAP) database based on the MySQL kernel. StoneDB can be seamlessly switched from MySQL. It provides features such as optimal performance and real-time analytics, offering you a one-stop solution to process online transaction processing (OLTP), online analytical processing (OLAP), and HTAP workloads.
Homepage: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;stonedb.io&#x2F;
Github repo: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;stoneatom&#x2F;stonedb
